fields.name: Monin 'SUGAR FREE' Caramel Syrup 1 Litre
fields.description:
Get ready for flavour so rich, it’s hard to believe it’s guilt-free. Our Sugar Free Caramel Syrup features the sweet, buttery, confectionery taste for lattes, frozen treats, whipped cream and unique cocktails.

Monin Sugar Free Caramel Syrup adds rich, smooth sweetness to lattes, cappuccinos, unique cocktails and desserts.

Monin Caramel Sugar Free is made with sucralose which is a no-calorie sweetener. Sucralose is derived directly from sugar: it offers a sweet sensation without the usual metallic aftertaste that you experience with other sweeteners. Indulge yourself with the sweet flavourful sensation of caramel… guilt free!

More Information 
1 Litre Plastic Bottle
SUGAR FREE
No Artificial Colouring or Preservatives
Optional Pumps are available that dispense 7.5ml (93 shots per bottle) for accurate and consistent measures
